<item>
            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-464] An HTTP &quot;204 NO CONTENT&quot; response results in dropped connection</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-464</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>After receiving a &amp;quot;204 NO CONTENT&amp;quot; response, HttpClient always closes the &lt;br/&gt;
connection.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
This did not happen in earlier versions and appears to have been caused by a &lt;br/&gt;
recent fix to bug# 34262.</description>
